# Code for Supplementary Material

This project is developed based on [sentence-transformers](https://github.com/UKPLab/sentence-transformers).

## Environment Setup

```
conda create -n emb python=3.10 -y
source activate emb
pip install -r requirements_emb.txt
pip install flash-attn==2.5.5
pip install -e .
pip install faiss
```

## Model Architecture

To inspect the model structure, run:

```
python tests/load_model.py
```

## Fine-tuning

To fine-tune the model, execute:

```
bash train/cl_mbert.sh
```

## Evaluation

To evaluate the model, run:

```
bash evaluation/evaluate.sh
```

## Note

Due to commercial reasons, we are currently unable to provide the training data and model weights. However, the provided code can help you understand and reproduce the core methodology.
